<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الذَّارِيَات<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَفْسِيرُ السُّورَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم , وَالذَّارِيَاتِ ذَرْوًا}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٣٩:</span> قَالَ عَلِيٌّ - عليه السلام -: الذَّارِيَاتُ: الرِّيَاحُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{تَذْرُوهُ}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: تُفَرِّقُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الذاريات: ١]<br>(٢) [الكهف: ٤٥]</p> </div>